any movie in this size range i always fix the index before watching it on a dvd player.  too many times have i been almost done a movie to have it just skip to the next movie. not just a pause and back to the scene.  i would then have to fix the index and reburn to a dvd-rw to watch in my dvd player.  i use "avi video joiner" under edit -> fix avi.

the program is a trial of 15 uses, but that is for joining files, so you can fix avi's index as long as you don't join more than 15 times.  seems to me like the movie that skips may have been 2 pieces joined and no index fixing, thus skipping to next track/movie.

now any movie over 700mb i fix before i even watch at all.

hope that helps
